lead_paragraph: Rookie Aaron Dell was more impressed with his teammates congratulating him than he was about his own performance. He even thanked the opposing coach, with who he worked with in the past.

headline.print_headline: Dell Gets First Career Shutout in Sharks' 2-0 Victory
